description:
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting new opportunity working within the Medical Directorate at Broomfield hospital recently rated as Good by the CQC. We are a dynamic team working to ensure high standards of care for all our patients and the development of our staff to enable them to reach their full potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The new role of Band 6 Clinical Practice Facilitator will support, facilitate and develop learning for all grades of staff within medical directorate with focus on promoting evidence based practice to meet the needs of patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;if you love to teach and enjoy helping others reach and exceed their development goals then this is a fantastic opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
